Class MapViewer

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.bananapuncher714.cartographer.core.map.MapViewer

  • public class MapViewer
extends java.lang.Object
    Individual per player settings that take priority over Cartographer's default settings but must conform to minimap settings. The player represented may or may not be online.
